      "content": "that's a great start, really hits the core of the argument. for the next section, i need to address the counter-arguments so i can debunk them. people usually bring up the idea of \"meritocracy\" and say it’s unfair to take from those who worked hard. how should i frame that argument in my essay so it doesn't undermine my main point? i want to show why the meritocracy argument is basically just a way to protect existing privilege.",
